text: Laksmi Shari De-Neefe Suardana (born January 29, 1996) is an Indonesian- Australian model, fashion designer, UNICEF activist, literacy book writer, and beauty pageant titleholder. She was crowned Puteri Indonesia 2022. She is the co-founder of the Ubud Writers and Readers Festival, the largest literacy festival in Southeast Asia. She will represent Indonesia at Miss Universe 2022. == References == Category:Indonesian writers Category:Indonesian activists Category:1996 births Category:Living people
